  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening education systems to promote healthy, peaceful and sustainable livelihoods in the West Africa Sahel</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">West Africa Sahel is a region, which faces extreme levels of vulnerability, affected by climate unpredictability, food insecurity, and conflicts. With more coordinated and systematic planning and monitoring, the region will have improved the implementation of SDG Target 4.7, including its integration into education policy, teaching, learning and monitoring, through strengthening MOEs&apos; capacities to equip children and young people with knowledge, skills and competencies to realize healthy, peaceful and sustainable livelihoods.</narrative>
  </description>
